  "text": "Instead of the initial five Gaps developed by Parasuraman, et al. [CITATION_1] which included users and provides, Zeithaml, et al. [CITATION_2] established five Gaps around the perception of users only based on tangibles, reliability, responsiveness, assurance and empathy. The Gap was based on the mean differences between users' expectations and perception.",
